ces. No further options, just the traffic stats are display and updated in realtime. <a href=\"http://www.binarytides.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2014/03/cbm.png\">Screenshot</a></li>","updatedAt":"2018-09-12T17:20:01.000Z"},{"awesomeListRepo":"caesar0301/awesome-pcaptools","categoryHTML":"<h2>Linux commands</h2>","itemHTML":"<li><strong>Tcptrack</strong>: is similar to iftop, and uses the pcap library to capture packets and calculate various statistics like the bandwidth used in each connection. It also supports the standard pcap filters that can be used to monitor specific connections. <a href=\"http://www.binarytides.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2014/03/tcptrack.png\">Screenshot</a></li>","updatedAt":"2018-09-12T17:20:01.000Z"},{"awesomeListRepo":"craftcms/awesome","categoryHTML":"<h2>Resources</h2><h3>Podcasts</h3>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"https://www.fostercommerce.com/podcast\">Commerce Minded</a> - A Craft Commerce-centric podcast that goes behind the scenes to chat with ecommerce merchants, developers, and vendors.</li>","updatedAt":"2018-09-12T13:46:20.000Z"},{"awesomeListRepo":"ahkscript/awesome-AutoHotkey","categoryHTML":"<h2>Libraries</h2><h3>Graphics</h3>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"https://github.com/mmikeww/AHKv2-Gdip\">AHKv2-GDIP</a><a data-role=\"trackawesomelist-badge\" href=\"https://github.com/mmikeww/AHKv2-Gdip\" style=\"text-decoration:none;top: -2px;position: relative;margin-left:4px;margin-right:4px;font-weight:400;\"><span style=\"color: #fff;font-size: 11px;font-family: Verdana, Geneva, DejaVu Sans,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"padding:4px 4px 4px 6px;background: #555;border-top-left-radius: 4px;border-bottom-left-radius: 4px;\">stars</span><span style=\"padding: 4px 6px 4px 4px;background: #007ec6;border-top-right-radius: 4px;border-bottom-right-radius: 4px;\">56</span></span></a><!--TRACK_AWESOME_REPO_ITEM_START____{\"type\":\"repo\",\"stargazerCount\":56,\"repo\":\"mmikeww/AHKv2-Gdip\"}____TRACK_AWESOME_REPO_ITEM_END--> - Update of the abo